content.text: The red arrow in the figure <image 1> belongs to the ______ stage of pregnancy.

The red arrow in the figure <image 1> belongs to the **embryonic** stage of pregnancy. This stage typically occurs from the third to the eighth week after conception, during which the major organs and body structures begin to form.
